le |last=Lester |first=Paul |title=Bastille (No 1,316) |date=25 July 2012 |accessdate=18 April 2013 |work=[[The Guardian]] |publisher=[[Guardian Media Group]] |archivedate=25 July 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725043222/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/jul/25/new-band-bastille |url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Format: Digital download\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Other People's Heartache#Part two|Other People's Heartache, Pt. 2]]''\n|\n* Released: December 2012 <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(UK)</span><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gigwise.com/news/78209/new-music-gabrielle-aplin-among-guests-on-new-bastille-mixtape |last=Baggs |first=Michael |title=New music: Gabrielle Aplin among guests on new Bastille mixtape |date=10 December 2012 |accessdate=18 April 2013 |publisher=[[Gigwise]]. Giant Digital |archivedate=9 May 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509035346/http://www.gigwise.com/news/78209/new-music-gabrielle-aplin-among-guests-on-new-bastille-mixtape |url-status=live |df=dmy }}</ref>\n* Format: Digital download\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Other People's Heartache#Part three|VS. (Other People's Heartache, {{nowrap|Pt. III)}}]]''\n|\n* Released: 8 December 2014<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/vs-other-peoples-heartache-pt-iii-mw0002771787 |title=VS. (Other People's Heartache, Pt. III) \u2013 Bastille |work=[[AllMusic]] |accessdate=28 October 2018 |author=Phares, Heather}}</ref>\n* Formats: CD, LP, digital download\n| 45 || 87 || 8 || 12\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Other People's Heartache#Part four|Other People's Heartache, Pt. 4]]''\n|\n* Released: 7 December 2018 <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(UK)</span><ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/other-peoples-heartache-pt-4/1444776657|title=Other People's Heartache, Pt. 4 by Other People's Heartache & Bastille|work=[[iTunes]] (UK)|accessdate=7 December 2018}}</ref>\n* Form